<!-- UTILITIES_TAB -->

<center>
<br>
<table class="zoovytable" width=800>
<tr class="zoovytableheader">
	<td>Account Utilities</td>
</tr>
<tr>
	<td>
	<i>With great power, comes great responsibility... -Uncle Ben</i><br>
<div class="hint">
So .. if you're seeing this page, then you were told about it by a member of Zoovy
Technical support.  Here you will find a collection of utilities which can
self-diagnose and self-resolve a number of interesting issues. 
These utilities *should* not be used as part of a normal day to day operation of a store, 
and indicate one or more bugs and/or nasty things that happens as a result of user error.
Please use carefully, and remember to make backups.<br>
</div>
<br>
<form id="thisFrm" name="thisFrm" action="/biz/batch/index.cgi">
<input type="hidden" name="VERB" value="NEW">
<input type="hidden" name="EXEC" value="UTILITY">
<input type="hidden" name="APP" value="">
<input type="hidden" name="GUID" value="<!-- GUID -->">
<input type="hidden" name=".function" value="">

<table>
<tr class="zoovysub1header">
	<td colspan=2>Products/Inventory</td>
</tr>
<tr>
	<td valign=top><input type="button" class="button"
		onClick="document.thisFrm.APP.value='PRODUCT_CLEANUP'; document.thisFrm.submit();" 
		value="Product Cleanup"></td>
	<td valign=top>
		Resets/Rebuilds Product Index, clears out deleted items from zoovy:prod_related, and zoovy:prod_accessories.
	</td>
</tr>
<tr>
	<td valign=top><input type="button" class="button"
		onClick="document.thisFrm.APP.value='INVENTORY_CLEANUP'; document.thisFrm.submit();" 
		value="Inventory Cleanup"></td>
	<td valign=top>
		Removes orphan inventory records which are not associated with a sku.
	</td>
</tr>
<tr class="zoovysub1header">
	<td colspan=2>eBay</td>
</tr>
<tr>
	<td valign=top><input type="button" class="button"
		onClick="
			document.thisFrm.APP.value='EBAY_UPDATE'; 
			document.thisFrm['.function'].value = 'enable-ebay-checkout';
			document.thisFrm.submit();" 
		value="Enable eBay Checkout"></td>
	<td valign=top>
		This does three things: 
		1. switches token setting, 
		2. attempts to revise all listings on the account, 
		3. sets global "EBAY-CHECKOUT" flag
	</td>
</tr>
<tr>
	<td valign=top><input type="button" class="button"
		onClick="
			document.thisFrm.APP.value='EBAY_UPDATE'; 
			document.thisFrm['.function'].value = 'end-all';
			document.thisFrm.submit();" 
		value="Close All Listings"></td>
	<td valign=top>
		Ends all active listings on eBay.
	</td>
</tr>
<tr>
	<td valign=top><input type="button" class="button" onClick="
			document.thisFrm.APP.value='EBAY_UPDATE'; 
			document.thisFrm['.function'].value = 'remove-checkout-all';
			document.thisFrm.submit();" 
		value="Remove Checkout"></td>
	<td valign=top>
		Removes all active listings on eBay.
	</td>
</tr>

<tr class="sub1header">
	<td>Tech Support Only</td>
</tr>
<tr>
	<td valign=top><input type="button" class="button" style="background-color: red; color: white;"
		onClick="document.thisFrm.APP.value='BIG_RED_BUTTON'; document.thisFrm.submit();" 
		value="** SUPPORT ONLY **"></td>
	<td valign=top>
		Do not push this button unless explicitly instructed to by technical support, 
		doing so could render your store in a non-functioning state.
	</td>
</tr>
</table>
</form>

</td></tr>
</table>
</center>

